1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:20,060
(Phoenix Mountain, Volume 1)

2
00:00:20,060 --> 00:00:20,900
(The Never-Ending Sky)

3
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:23,710
You must be
enjoying yourself, Master Liang.

4
00:00:23,710 --> 00:00:24,830
Airing out your scripts?

5
00:00:27,070 --> 00:00:29,440
No wonder

6
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:31,350
my left eyelid kept twitching
all morning.

7
00:00:32,110 --> 00:00:33,650
=Cases Between Us=
I was wondering

8
00:00:33,664 --> 00:00:35,520
what the good news would be.

9
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:39,200
=Episode 31=
Here it comes.

10
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:40,640
Don't get your hopes high.

11
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,320
We'd like to ask about someone.

12
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:46,320
Master Ma Xiangde.

13
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,790
We heard you knew him.

14
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:48,750
Come on.

15
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:51,296
Who in Liulichang Antique Market
hasn't done business with me?

16
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,070
We weren't close.

17
00:00:54,030 --> 00:00:55,880
How did Master Ma make his fortune?

18
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:58,000
We weren't close,

19
00:00:58,350 --> 00:01:00,320
but since Chief Yuan's asking,

20
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,670
I do know a little.

21
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,000
I heard

22
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,560
that when they

23
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:10,680
were returning from Xi'an to Beijing,

24
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,790
they hired an escort agency

25
00:01:11,790 --> 00:01:13,200
to protect the family.

26
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:16,680
Something happened

27
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:18,870
along the way.

28
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:23,000
As soon as they reached Fangshan,

29
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:26,070
the Ma's heirloom blood jade pendant

30
00:01:26,070 --> 00:01:27,400
suddenly vanished.

31
00:01:27,710 --> 00:01:29,430
It was an imperial gift.

32
00:01:29,430 --> 00:01:30,864
Losing it was a serious offense.

33
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,510
The escort captain,

34
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,560
Guo Mengzhi,

35
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,640
had to pay a fortune in compensation.

36
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,590
It ruined him.

37
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,920
Are you sure about that?

38
00:01:45,870 --> 00:01:46,640
Si.

39
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,680
That's the escort agency's address.

40
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,680
Go see for yourselves.

41
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:07,180
(Sanqin Escort Agency,
No. 53, Tangzi Alley)

42
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:09,980
(Sanqin Escort Agency)

43
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:15,400
Looks like Liang Can
wasn't lying this time.

44
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,800
According to the agency,

45
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,030
before the escort began,

46
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,520
no one had actually seen

47
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,360
that the jade pendant
was among the valuables.

48
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:25,630
The Ma family got rich

49
00:02:25,776 --> 00:02:27,310
off Captain Guo's compensation.

50
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:30,400
Maybe it was a setup from the start.

51
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,030
Something's fishy.

52
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,870
Could Ma Yuzhen's murder

53
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,520
be an act of revenge?

54
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,310
Miss Qiu and the Guo family...

55
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:54,150
Yes,

56
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,910
you're right.

57
00:02:56,096 --> 00:02:57,590
I was born into that escort family.

58
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:59,360
Guo Mengzhi was my father.

59
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,520
The compensation bankrupted us.

60
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:03,960
We changed our names,

61
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:05,470
left our hometown,

62
00:03:05,888 --> 00:03:06,910
and lived in poverty,

63
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,240
burdened with debt.

64
00:03:08,464 --> 00:03:10,448
There was only enough money
to raise one child.

65
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,800
I was then sent to an orphanage.

66
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:14,630
I never saw

67
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,120
my parents or my younger brother again.

68
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:19,560
You hated the Ma family,

69
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,120
so you killed Ma Yuzhen.

70
00:03:22,590 --> 00:03:24,680
You think I only found out today

71
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,400
that the Ma family framed my family?

72
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,150
If I'd wanted revenge,

73
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:29,960
do you think

74
00:03:30,576 --> 00:03:32,528
anyone in the Ma family
would still be alive?

75
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:36,280
Look at this.

76
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,030
The jade is fake.

77
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:44,470
Yes. It's fake.

78
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,470
But the real blood jade pendant

79
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:48,300
wasn't lost by the Sanqin Escort Agency.

80
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:49,310
So?

81
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:52,910
During the Boxer Rebellion,

82
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,960
you fled to Xi'an with your daughter.

83
00:03:57,104 --> 00:03:59,000
You were starving
and collapsed by the roadside,

84
00:03:59,056 --> 00:04:01,190
yet you still wouldn't
trade the pendant for food.

85
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,590
Because by then,

86
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:07,000
the real pendant had already been lost.

87
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:08,750
Without proof,

88
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:10,080
it's just your word.

89
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:12,120
At worst,
you expose this pendant as fake

90
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,870
and ruin the Ma family's reputation.

91
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,840
Everyone will know

92
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:18,070
the Sanqin Escort Agency
lost the shipment.

93
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:21,040
Then your father's former workers
won't be able to make a living either.

94
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:23,360
We all go down together.

95
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,160
Just because the Ma family

96
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,680
wronged my family

97
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,680
doesn't mean

98
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:32,920
you can pin a murder on me.

99
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,040
Young Master Zhao,

100
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,464
the fatal wound was indeed unusual.

101
00:04:54,464 --> 00:04:56,270
I found something important
in the second autopsy.

102
00:04:56,288 --> 00:04:56,920
At first glance,

103
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,640
it looked like she died
from a hammer blow.

104
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:00,128
But during the second examination,

105
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:02,680
I found several horizontal
fractures on her skull

106
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:05,000
interrupted by the vertical crack,
forming a T-shape.

107
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,040
That means

108
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:10,480
the same spot was struck twice.

109
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,510
Think about it.

110
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:12,070
If the victim

111
00:05:12,070 --> 00:05:13,630
had still been conscious

112
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:14,680
after the first blow,

113
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,870
she would've tried to dodge.

114
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,270
The odds of the second blow

115
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:19,270
landing in the exact
same place are almost zero.

116
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,720
With that in mind,

117
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,040
I examined the wound more closely.

118
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,000
The result?

119
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,120
She was

120
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,070
already dead

121
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,310
when the first blow landed.

122
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,750
So the second blow

123
00:05:27,750 --> 00:05:29,750
was only meant to cover up
the original wound.

124
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,270
I have a theory.

125
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,310
You mentioned

126
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,280
a jade inkstone before.

127
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,270
I think that was the real murder weapon.

128
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:43,940
(Division Four Chief's Office)

129
00:05:44,688 --> 00:05:46,816
If the green jade inkstone
was the murder weapon,

130
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,870
then Shunzi is our prime suspect.

131
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,680
But he has an alibi.

132
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:53,630
Did he bribe Mrs. Qi?

133
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:57,680
Chief Yuan. Young Master Zhao.

134
00:05:57,830 --> 00:05:59,070
Someone came in and confessed.

135
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:00,480
Shunzi?

136
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,390
Shunzi was my informant

137
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:17,920
inside the Ma Jade Shop.

138
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,510
The Ma family's downfall

139
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,310
was an inside job.

140
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:26,040
That day, I killed Ma Yuzhen
with the jade inkstone.

141
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,070
Shunzi saw everything.

142
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,560
To protect me,

143
00:06:29,824 --> 00:06:32,064
he used the hammer
to cover up the original wound

144
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:35,120
and framed Shi Litai.

145
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:37,360
Then I stole the inkstone

146
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,040
and cleaned up the scene.

147
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,240
If you did it,

148
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,568
why didn't you confess yesterday?

149
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,880
Why wait until today?

150
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,950
My conscience finally caught up with me.

151
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:02,630
Miss Qiu said

152
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:04,270
she suddenly grew a conscience.

153
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,360
She must be lying.

154
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:08,390
But every detail she gave

155
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,120
checks out.

156
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,510
So what's she after?

157
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,600
We need to find Shunzi.

158
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:16,920
He's the key to this.

159
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:19,120
Chief.

160
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,696
Someone else came in and surrendered.

161
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:25,390
You said you killed Ma Yuzhen?

162
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:27,870
I lied.

163
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,630
I didn't steal

164
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,070
the green jade inkstone.

165
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,480
Who is there?

166
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:43,000
That night, I was hiding in the attic.

167
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,240
I saw Ma Yuzhen suddenly faint.

168
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:52,750
Then Ma Buyan snuck in,

169
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:55,160
searched the place
from top to bottom, and left.

170
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,480
So I climbed down

171
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:03,040
to look for the blood jade pendant.

172
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,950
Just then, Ma Yuzhen woke up

173
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:05,870
and caught me.

174
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,040
What are you doing?

175
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,368
Where's the blood jade pendant?

176
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:13,920
What do you want?

177
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:15,190
I want to know.

178
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,630
Fifteen years ago,

179
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:18,430
on that escort from Xi'an to Beijing,

180
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,680
was the pendant really lost,

181
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,680
or did your father frame us?

182
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,120
You're Captain Guo's son

183
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,870
from the Sanqin Escort Agency?

184
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,670
Then you should know

185
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,630
this pendant is fake.

186
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:35,440
The real one

187
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,840
was lost on that shipment.

188
00:08:36,864 --> 00:08:38,250
Your escort agency was responsible.

189
00:08:38,272 --> 00:08:39,750
My father worked his whole life,

190
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:43,510
and he still died
without paying off those debts.

191
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:47,000
If so, you can take
this green jade inkstone instead.

192
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,510
(Old-Pit Duan stone from Zhongyan)
It's a masterpiece.

193
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:49,600
Worth a fortune.

194
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,510
Don't worry.

195
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:52,360
I won't call the police.

196
00:08:53,270 --> 00:08:55,960
Take it as our family's way
of making things right.

197
00:09:02,550 --> 00:09:04,720
But the farther I walked,
the more uneasy I became.

198
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,870
My father lost everything,

199
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:08,670
yet never took a dime that wasn't his.

200
00:09:09,030 --> 00:09:10,630
If I sold this inkstone for money,

201
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:13,136
how would I be any different
from the Ma family that ruined us?

202
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:15,120
I couldn't keep it.

203
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,750
But then...

204
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:22,200
Shunzi is the only one
who uses this hammer.

205
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,150
His fingerprints are all over it.

206
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,120
Call the police later.

207
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,360
Once they find the green jade inkstone

208
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:29,790
and match his fingerprints,

209
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:31,320
who'd believe

210
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,320
he didn't steal the rest?

211
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:37,510
Once the theft is confirmed
and the items are declared missing,

212
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:40,240
the insurance company
will have to pay in full.

213
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,240
That's great, Yuzhen.

214
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:44,960
Now that we have a scapegoat,

215
00:09:45,270 --> 00:09:47,720
our plan can't fail.

216
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,910
Who would've thought

217
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:51,720
being a scapegoat runs in the family?

218
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,360
Go on.

219
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:56,750
Okay.

220
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:57,840
Careful.

221
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:16,720
Why are you back?

222
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,840
I never imagined
they could be this vicious.

223
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,960
They destroyed my family

224
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,510
and then tried to use me, too.

225
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,600
After all that,
how could I not kill her?

226
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,870
Guo Mengzhi was your father, too?

227
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,840
So Miss Qiu is your sister.

228
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:42,080
I killed her.

229
00:10:42,192 --> 00:10:43,856
My sister had nothing to do with it.

230
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,960
She only hit Ma Yuzhen with the hammer

231
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,320
to cover up what I'd done.

232
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:56,200
Just then, Shi Litai walked in.

233
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:58,440
She thought on her feet and framed him.

234
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,510
When my family fell apart,

235
00:11:01,904 --> 00:11:03,744
we could only afford to keep one child.

236
00:11:04,368 --> 00:11:05,790
My sister was the one left behind.

237
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:08,360
She suffered everything in my place.

238
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:11,480
I won't let her
take the blame for me again.

239
00:11:32,862 --> 00:11:38,022
(Jingshi Police Department)

240
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,030
Chief Yuan.

241
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,750
Miss Qiu.

242
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:50,240
Thank you for hiring a lawyer
for my brother.

243
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,840
The lawyer said Shunzi
acted in the heat of the moment.

244
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,900
There were extenuating
circumstances. He'll probably

245
00:11:54,912 --> 00:11:55,910
only serve two years.

246
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,270
I left Kobayashi's company.

247
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:04,840
If you need anything,

248
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:06,320
just let us know.

249
00:12:10,498 --> 00:12:11,240
Chief Yuan,

250
00:12:11,550 --> 00:12:12,960
may I have a word?

251
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:23,420
(Jingshi Police Department)

252
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:33,670
What did Miss Qiu want to tell you?

253
00:12:36,352 --> 00:12:37,870
She asked me to have the prison guards

254
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:39,000
look after her brother.

255
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,390
Really? Then why keep it from me?

256
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:43,630
No idea.

257
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:46,240
Maybe she's just cautious.

258
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:49,390
Makes sense.

259
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,870
In this case, the killer was the victim,

260
00:12:56,270 --> 00:12:57,390
while the victim

261
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:59,000
was the real villain.

262
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:01,150
The more I think about

263
00:13:01,184 --> 00:13:02,240
Miss Qiu and Shunzi,

264
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,750
the worse I feel.

265
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,510
Lately, three words

266
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,270
keep coming to mind.

267
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,080
Which three?

268
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,630
"Had no choice."

269
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:29,720
The truly evil

270
00:13:30,870 --> 00:13:33,840
and the purely good are both rare.

271
00:13:34,390 --> 00:13:39,030
Most people
just get swept along by fate.

272
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:41,870
Right.

273
00:13:42,736 --> 00:13:44,030
Fate works in mysterious ways.

274
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:45,840
Yes.

275
00:13:47,136 --> 00:13:48,448
Fate works in mysterious ways.

276
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:03,550
What if one day

277
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:05,750
you and I ended up on opposite sides?

278
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,030
What would you do?

279
00:14:07,712 --> 00:14:08,720
What are you planning?

280
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,960
Murder?

281
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,030
Helping criminals?

282
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,670
I haven't lost my mind.

283
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:18,270
I'm just saying.

284
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:25,120
If that happens,

285
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,600
tell me first.

286
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,150
I can help you.

287
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,390
But from your point of view,

288
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:46,750
if I crossed the line,

289
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,512
wouldn't you have to arrest me?

290
00:14:49,390 --> 00:14:50,910
Or if you couldn't stop me,

291
00:14:50,944 --> 00:14:52,128
you bring me to justice.

292
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:53,510
But you're Yuan Hong.

293
00:15:09,792 --> 00:15:10,910
You just said it yourself.

294
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,130
Fate works in mysterious ways.

295
00:15:12,150 --> 00:15:12,870
You...

296
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:13,480
Come on.

297
00:15:13,910 --> 00:15:14,670
Where are we going?

298
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:16,870
The case is closed.

299
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:18,150
Your injury is healed.

300
00:15:18,150 --> 00:15:19,200
Time to move you out.

301
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,870
Why are you in such a hurry?

302
00:15:21,632 --> 00:15:23,392
Tomorrow is the Chinese New Year's Eve.

303
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,320
I'm not.

304
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,200
Your parents are.

305
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:25,840
Let's go.

306
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,720
Says the guy

307
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:30,630
who doesn't even celebrate that.

308
00:15:30,630 --> 00:15:32,080
Petty guy.

309
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:44,860
(Xu Residence)

310
00:15:44,870 --> 00:15:45,720
Secretary Xu.

311
00:15:46,510 --> 00:15:47,600
One moment, Secretary Xu.

312
00:15:50,670 --> 00:15:51,510
Minister Zhao.

313
00:15:52,096 --> 00:15:52,750
Secretary Xu.

314
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:53,630
What is it?

315
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:57,200
The professors from Peking,
Tsinghua, and Yenching

316
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:59,390
have jointly petitioned us.

317
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:01,240
If their salaries aren't paid soon,

318
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:02,750
they'll all go on strike.

319
00:16:03,390 --> 00:16:04,150
Minister Zhao,

320
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:06,390
that's an Education Ministry matter.

321
00:16:06,390 --> 00:16:08,030
Why come to me?

322
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:10,440
The funding still hasn't been approved,

323
00:16:10,512 --> 00:16:12,336
and the Cabinet keeps passing the buck.

324
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:14,150
I'm out of options.

325
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:15,840
I was hoping you could give me

326
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,870
a straight answer.

327
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:22,270
Minister Zhao,

328
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:24,000
times are difficult.

329
00:16:24,390 --> 00:16:27,390
General Chen's military expenses
are enormous.

330
00:16:27,790 --> 00:16:30,080
I hope you'll see the bigger picture.

331
00:16:32,270 --> 00:16:33,080
I see.

332
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:34,870
Impressive.

333
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:35,910
You even make embezzlement

334
00:16:36,630 --> 00:16:39,080
sound respectable.

335
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,440
If you think it's unfair,

336
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:41,960
you're welcome to file a complaint.

337
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:42,910
I hear your son

338
00:16:43,150 --> 00:16:45,240
has grown quite close

339
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,480
to the Marshal's son.

340
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:49,390
Still, if you're willing to compromise,

341
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:51,750
General Chen
thinks very highly of your abilities.

342
00:16:52,270 --> 00:16:54,080
If we're all rowing
in the same direction,

343
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,790
those funds you mentioned

344
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:58,080
are nothing more

345
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,320
than an accounting adjustment.

346
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:03,750
Secretary Xu,

347
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:06,640
I only want to do my job.

348
00:17:06,656 --> 00:17:08,500
I have no interest
in political infighting.

349
00:17:08,816 --> 00:17:09,960
Then, when the missing funds

350
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,510
are investigated,

351
00:17:12,110 --> 00:17:14,310
Minister Zhao,
you'll be the one held responsible.

352
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:15,830
Wait.

353
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:17,480
You embezzle public funds,

354
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:18,880
but you threaten me?

355
00:17:19,070 --> 00:17:20,160
What kind of logic is that?

356
00:17:20,350 --> 00:17:22,110
You've misunderstood.

357
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:24,400
Our families

358
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:26,000
have a deep bond.

359
00:17:26,496 --> 00:17:28,900
Just a few days ago,
your son risked his life to save me.

360
00:17:28,912 --> 00:17:30,750
He was badly wounded and nearly killed.

361
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,720
I've barely slept since.

362
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:36,880
How could you call that a threat?

363
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,240
Chief Yuan,

364
00:17:51,750 --> 00:17:53,310
are you investigating Kobayashi?

365
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:55,350
His business partner in Beijing

366
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:56,830
is backed by the military.

367
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,240
They're holding

368
00:17:58,240 --> 00:18:00,112
a secret meeting tonight
at a private estate.

369
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,440
I know a back path.

370
00:18:01,504 --> 00:18:02,752
It'll take you past the guards

371
00:18:02,784 --> 00:18:04,280
and straight into the inner courtyard.

372
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:06,350
Why are you telling me this?

373
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:08,960
Chief Yuan,

374
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:12,200
in times like these,
good people deserve a good ending.

375
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:16,400
I wish you the best of luck.

376
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:27,020
(Jizhi)

377
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:35,020
(End of Episode 31)

378
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:38,040
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

379
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:39,580
♪Troubled times
are but a laughing matter♪

380
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:40,830
♪However, the world changes♪

381
00:18:40,830 --> 00:18:42,750
♪You'll still be by my side♪

382
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,440
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

383
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:46,010
♪Praise and blame come and go♪

384
00:18:46,010 --> 00:18:47,580
♪If this is my final chapter♪

385
00:18:47,580 --> 00:18:50,080
♪I'll solve this mystery with you♪
